"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-the-internet-is-obsessed-with-botswana-star-tebogo-after-paris-2024-heroics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8925525744721406, \"rank\": 0.12007248787040088, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbThe internet is OBSESSED with Botswana superstar Letsile Tebogo, and rightly so  Sprinting excellence.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8925525744721406, \"rank\": 0.12007248787040088, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 4.4124267031910366e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Letsile Tebogo wrote himself into Botswana folklore with a run for the ages at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 4.4124267031910366e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The internet is in raptures.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"21-year-old Letsile Tebogo produced the run of his life to claim gold in a much-anticipated 200m event.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the fastest qualifier and the only man to go under 20 seconds in the semi-finals, so he was certainly expected to medal.\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, 100m champion andAmerican superstar Noah Lyleswas the overwhelming favourite to claim gold alongside his compatriot Kenny Bednarek.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Tebogo ripped up the script and stormed to the line first in 19.46 seconds ahead of Bednarek in 19.62 and Lyles in 19.70.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo is the first African man to win this event and it's also the first gold medal in Botswana's history at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 4.4124267031910366e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Touchingly, Tebogo revealed the birthdate of his late mother on his running shoes in the moments after claiming what must have been a truly emotional victory.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In case you have been living under a rock and missed this staggering sprinting performance, check it out here.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This man is trending all over the internet and rightly so.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Letsile Tebogo is the fifth-fastest man over the 200m distance in history.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Usain Bolt's mark of 19.19 still sits at the top of the pile, followed by his fellow Jamaican Yohan Blake with 19.26, Lyles who ran 19.31 in Oregon last year and the legendary Michael Johnson's 19.32 set in 1996.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}, {\"begin\": 1566, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999999489723463, \"rank\": 5.1027432627896964e-08, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yohan_Blake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yohan Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yohan_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yohan_Blake\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.8331841170795686, \"rank\": 0.20020567886057086, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"View the full schedule via the Paris 2024official website.\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973288141, \"rank\": 2.6711569129459092e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.com.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, you can also send a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.960860136359199, \"rank\": 0.04073419445754922, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor your social fix.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999963676411913, \"rank\": 3.6297878880521455e-06, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 1991, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9997531133511002, \"rank\": 0.00021383083995815485, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource